title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 645-4.10 - Report

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 645-4.10 - Report

State Regulations

Following the close of the record, including receipt of
the transcript, if any, the hearing officer shall prepare and submit to the
commission a hearing report, which shall become part of the
record. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
645-4.10

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
